metadata.description:
SIMONIKA - JELLYFISH #2. 
CLOSER. EXPLORING THE MICROVERSE OF THINGS. 
The "Closer" collection explores the very detail of things. By doing so, new microverses will arise for the observer. The observation will unlock something new, dissolved from the original meaning, which reveals the beauty of structures, consistency, light and colors. Photography by simonika. simonika.art.
